sequelize model:generate --name=user --attributes=first_name:string,last_name:string,email:string,password:string,profile_img:text
sequelize model:generate --name=bottle --attributes=type:string,img_url:text
sequelize model:generate --name=cocktail --attributes=name:string,img_url:text
sequelize model:generate --name=rating --attributes=rating:integer,userId:integer,cocktailId:integer
sequelize model:generate --name=comment --attributes=comment:text,userId:integer,cocktailId:integer
sequelize model:generate --name=users_bottles --attributes=userId:integer,bottleId:integer
sequelize model:generate --name=users_cocktails --attributes=userId:integer,cocktailId:integer
sequelize model:generate --name=bottles_cocktails --attributes=bottleId:integer,cocktailId:integer


users belongs to many bottles (vice versa) through

users belongs to many cocktails (vice versa) through

bottles belongs to many cocktails (vice versa) through

users has many ratings, ratings belongs to user
cocktails has many ratings, ratings belongs to cocktail

users has many comments, comments belongs to user
cocktails has many comments, comments belongs to cocktail






